Hi all, I am looking to sell my T211 Red Suns.  Something for everyone here, whether you are looking for a nice type card, to upgrade your existing set, or just a low grade to fill a hole in your collection, I have a great group from which to choose.  I accept PayPal, check or MO for these.  Prices are net to me, so please add 3% for regular PayPal.  Domestic shipping is free.  Shipping to other countries, I will work with you on price.

Additional scans available on request.
